<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/28668713">铜雀台的「雀」字作何解？和朱雀的含义一样吗？为什么不用凤鸾等祥瑞字眼而用「雀」呢？如果通「爵」又何解？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3650463" data-action="/question/detail">

